                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">Type</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">QueryFieldType</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground"><code>Text</code>, <code>Number</code>, <code>Date</code>, <code>Boolean</code>, or <code>Select</code>. Determines the default operator set and the built-in value editor.</td></tr>
