                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-border/40">
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">QueryNode</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">abstract</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">Base of the tree — either a <code>QueryRule</code> (leaf) or a <code>QueryGroup</code> (branch).</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">QueryRule.Field</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">string</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">The <code>QueryField.Name</code> this rule targets.</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">QueryRule.Operator</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">string</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">One of the field's allowed operator keys.</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">QueryRule.Value / Value2</td><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">object?</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">The comparison value(s). <code>Value2</code> is used only by range operators ("between").</td></tr>
