                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">Number</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground"><code>=</code>, <code>!=</code>, <code>&lt;</code> less than, <code>&lt;=</code>, <code>&gt;</code> greater than, <code>&gt;=</code>, <code>between</code>, <code>isNull</code>, <code>isNotNull</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">Date</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground"><code>=</code>, <code>!=</code>, <code>&lt;</code>, <code>&lt;=</code>, <code>&gt;</code>, <code>&gt;=</code>, <code>between</code>, <code>isNull</code>, <code>isNotNull</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">Boolean</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground"><code>=</code>, <code>!=</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">Select</td><td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground"><code>=</code>, <code>!=</code>, <code>in</code>, <code>notIn</code>, <code>isNull</code>, <code>isNotNull</code> (<code>in</code>/<code>notIn</code> take a comma-separated value)</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </Stack>
            <Lumeo.Text Size="sm" Color="muted" Class="mt-3"><code>isEmpty</code> / <code>isNotEmpty</code> / <code>isNull</code> / <code>isNotNull</code> render no value editor; <code>between</code> renders two. Override the set per field via <code>QueryField.Operators</code>.</Lumeo.Text>
        </Stack>
    </Stack>
</Stack>

